Count 0218: Hubei filial piety demand complete blocking in place, Wuhan is still to be observed.
数说疫情0218：湖北孝感要求彻底阻隔到位，武汉仍待观察。
Count 0218: Hubei filial piety demand complete blocking in place, Wuhan is still to be observed.
