An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
今天起我们将不再提“归零”，以期警钟长鸣2020年1月17日，医护人员将患者送至武汉金银潭医院。
From today we will no longer mention "home to zero" in the hope that the alarm bells will ring on January 17, 2020, medical personnel will send the patients to Wuhan gold and silver pool hospital.
摄影/无畏文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑|谢丽容一、全国累计确诊病例变动趋势截至2月17日24:00，全国累计报告确诊新冠肺炎病例72436例。
At 24: 00 on February 17, a cumulative total of 72,436 new cases of newly diagnosed pneumonia were reported nationwide. At 2400 hours on February 17, the nation as a whole reported a total of 72,436 new cases of confirmed cases.
以下为分区趋势图。
The following is the zoning trend chart.
图1国内非湖北地区有趋稳态势，武汉仍令人担忧。
Fig. 1 There is trend of stabilization in non-Hubei area, Wuhan is still worrying.
二、新增病例：国内非湖北地区继续坚定下降，武汉待观察图2 国内非湖北新增病例今天降至接近100以内，希望魔鬼就要被关进笼子。
The number of new cases in non-Hubei areas of China continues to decline steadily. Figure 2 shows that the number of new cases in non-Hubei province fell to nearly 100 today, hoping the devil will be caged.
接受部分网友忠告，今天起小编不再提“归零”，以期警钟长鸣。
Accept some netizens advice, today no longer mention "back to zero", with a view to warning bells.
敬畏科学：正如 Y=r^X 函数本身所显示的，可以无限逼近零，却永远不会归零。
Science in awe: As the Y = r ^ X function itself shows, it is infinitely close to zero, but never to zero.
病毒应该只能控制却无法消灭。
The virus should be contained but not eliminated.
母体一旦产生便只可隔离却不能“撤除”。
Once the mother is born, it can only be isolated but not "removed."
很多人担心非湖北地区会否有些新的疫情爆发地。
Many worry whether there will be new outbreaks in non-Hubei areas.
我们今天看看紧邻湖北的河南。
We have a look at Henan next to Hubei today.
图2.1图2.2 河南每日新增病例柱状河南约在2月3日经过峰值，其后下降，但至今仍在两位数水平。
Figure 2.1. 2. 2. 2. 2. 2. A new daily case in Henan province peaked on about February 3 and then declined, but is still in double digits.
图2.3 信阳每日新增病例柱状数据显示信阳疫情峰值已过，已连续八天在个位数波动。
Fig. 2.3 The columnar data of Xinyang daily cases showed that the peak of Xinyang epidemic had been exceeded and had fluctuated in single digits for eight consecutive days.
信阳离武汉最近，也是河南受疫情影响最严重的地区。
Xinyang is located near Wuhan and is the worst affected area in Henan Province.
昨天新闻有报信阳新县出现两起“超异常”案例，为此，位于大别山的新县已确定将所有有湖北接触史的居民延长居家隔离延长至21天。
In response to news reports yesterday of two "super-abnormal" cases in Yangxin County, the new county in Dabie Mountain has decided to extend the stay-at-home isolation of all residents with a history of Hubei to 21 days.
图3湖北非武汉地区新增继续下降，显示防控措施有效。
Fig. 3 The increase of non-Wuhan area in Hubei province continued to decrease.
我们看看紧邻武汉的重灾区孝感、黄冈。
We look next to Wuhan's disaster areas of filial piety, Huanggang.
图3.1孝感每日新增病例柱状2月12日统计口径调整对孝感影响较小，之后延续下降趋势，但相比黄冈似有差距。
Figure 3.1 Filial Feeling Daily New Cases Columns Feb. 12 Statistical adjustment had little effect on filial piety, and then continued to decline, but there seems to be a gap compared with Huanggang.
孝感病例在疫情早期低于黄冈，后来反超，值得推敲。
Filial piety cases in the early stage of the epidemic lower than Huanggang, later overtook, worthy of deliberation.
另据新华社：湖北省孝感市疫情防控指挥部2月16日部署对全市疫情防控发起全面总攻，要求彻底排查管控到位，彻底阻隔到位，做到应收尽收、应隔尽隔，所有确诊患者集中救治、疑似患者集中收治、发热患者集中留观、密切接触者隔离观察。
According to Xinhua News Agency: February 16, Xiaoyan City, Hubei Province, the command and control of the epidemic launched a comprehensive attack on the city's epidemic prevention and control, requiring thorough checks and control in place, complete isolation, all confirmed patients concentrated treatment, suspected patients concentrated treatment, fever patients concentrated observation, close contacts quarantined observation.
图3.2黄冈每日新增病例黄冈曾经被视为“第二个武汉”的疫情高发地，已经连续3天在个位数，昨天实现零新增。
Fig. 3.2 Huanggang daily new cases Huanggang was once regarded as the "second Wuhan" high-incidence area, has been in the single digits for three days, yesterday achieved zero new cases.
黄冈的新增病例峰值比湖北非武汉地区早出现了4天左右（第二个峰值是统计口径调整所致），是否意味着其在待排查、待收治方面的严重短板问题暴露较早？早暴露换来早解决。
The peak of new cases in Huanggang was about 4 days earlier than in non-Wuhan area of Huanggang (the second peak was due to statistical adjustment).
图4武汉数据仍令人忧心忡忡。
Figure 4. Wuhan data still gives cause for concern.
据报近日武汉又在落实五个“百分之百”：确诊患者应收尽收、疑似患者核酸检测、发热病人隔离、小区村庄封闭管理。
Wuhan is reported to have recently implemented five "100 percent": confirmed patients receivable, suspected patients nucleic acid testing, fever patients isolation, small village closed management.
说明此前仍存遗漏。
Explanation still missing before.
传染病防控就像堵水管子，百分之一的漏，就是漏！不全堵上，满盘皆失。
Infectious disease control is like a water-blocking pipe, 1% leakage, is leakage! Not all plugged up, full plate is lost.
希望在全国支持下，在新领导班子的统筹安排下，武汉人民这次能过这一关。
I hope that with the support of the whole country, under the overall arrangement of the new leadership, the people of Wuhan can pass this test.
武汉挺住！三、武汉仍在较高水平图5国内非湖北地区增速降至0.66%，湖北非武汉地区的病例增速降至1.22%，武汉仍在较高水平。
Wuhan is still at a high level Figure 5 Domestic non-Hubei region growth rate fell to 0.66%, Hubei non-Wuhan region to 1.22%, Wuhan is still high level.
四、国内非湖北地区密切接触者追踪力度：湖北有所上升，存量继续下降图6国内非湖北地区该项指标持续提升，显示彻底阻隔的能力和决心。
Close contacts in non-Hubei areas of China: Hubei has been on the rise and stocks continue to decline. Figure 6 The indicator continues to rise in non-Hubei areas of China, demonstrating the ability and determination to completely separate.
湖北这个指标总体一直微弱，显示其对密切接触者追踪力度与全国有较大差距，遗憾的是，我们至今看不到武汉的数据。
Hubei this index has been weak overall, showing that it is close contacts with the national tracking efforts have a large gap, unfortunately, we have not seen Wuhan data.
图7湖北尚在接受医学观察者存量数据出现继续下降，有疫情趋缓因素，也有追踪力度不够的因素。
Fig. 7 The stock data of medical observers in Hubei province continued to decline. There were factors of slowing the epidemic and insufficient tracking.
国内非湖北地区继续下降降幅加大。
The decline in non-Hubei areas continued to increase.
五、疑似病例新增和存量继续下降图8湖北和国内非湖北地区每日新增疑似病例继续下降！图9疑似病例存量都在下降。
Figure 8 The number of new suspected cases per day continues to decrease in Hubei and non-Hubei areas.
六、国内非湖北地区在院治疗人数图10湖北在院治疗人数仍有较大上升，交叉印证可推定武汉的收治能力在提高。
Figure 10 The number of people treated in hospitals in Hubei Province is still on the rise. The cross-examination shows that the treatment capacity of Wuhan is improving.
七、新增治愈人数上升，病死率也在回升图11每日新增治愈人数各有起伏。
Increase in the number of new cures and recovery of the fatality rate Figure 11 The number of new daily treatments varies.
图12病死率继续回升，这有病死发生时间与新确诊增加不同步因素。
Figure 12 The mortality rate continues to rise, with an increase in asynchronous factors between the onset of disease and new diagnoses.
也有救治能力和医疗资源因素。
There are also therapeutic and medical resource factors.
武汉病死率仍明显高于湖北和全国。
Wuhan fatality rate is still significantly higher than Hubei and China.
小结：武汉以外地区继续好转，仍有一些局部值得关注。
Summary: Wuhan outside the region to continue to improve, there are still some parts of concern.
武汉再次部署落实五个“百分之百”，意在“尽收尽治”、“彻底阻隔”。
Wuhan re-deployment of the implementation of five "100 percent", intended to "do as much as possible", "complete isolation."
期待此举成功！● 数说疫情数说疫情0217：湖北以外新增病例4日内归零，武汉再现波动数说疫情0216：湖北化解堰塞湖战局扭转，非湖北地区新增病例5日内清零数说疫情0215：非湖北地区新增病例5日后有望清零，湖北进入总攻阶段数说疫情0214：国内非湖北地区疫情已出现“关键拐点”数说疫情0213：今天只说湖北，武汉“堰塞湖”显形了数说疫情0212：武汉形势扭转，湖北夺回主动权，全国继续向好▲点击图片查看更多疫情报道责编| 黄端 duanhuang@caijing.com.cn本文为《财经》杂志原创文章，未经授权不得转载或建立镜像。
